    <h1>Sphere manipulation module</h1>
      <h2>Sphere creation</h2>
        <p> When dealing with spherical functions/distributions such as Orientation Distribution Function is becomes important
        to have appropriate spheres whether is is for visualisation or computation purpose.
        This module regroups several process to build visualisation spheres (icosphere) and spheres used specially in MRI (symmetric spheress) to take into account
        signal antipodal symmetry.</p>
        Please report to the documentation of each process for more details:
        <ul>
          <li><a href="bvrocess://BuildIcoSphere"><bvProcessName name="BuildIcosphere"/></a></li>
          <li><a href="bvrocess://BuildRepulsionSphere"><bvProcessName name="BuildRepulsionSphere"/></a></li>
          <li><a href="bvrocess://BuildSymmetricRepulsionSphere"><bvProcessName name="BuildSymmetricRepulsionSphere"/></a></li>
        </ul>
  </xhtml>
